Section 9
    Lecture 59: JPA Embedded Entities

1. Refactoring
 1.1 Create New Entity Class named Address: ej.springframework.domain.Address.java
 1.2 Add @Embeddable annotation on the Address Class
 1.3 Remove relative previous address fields in the Customer class
 1.4 Add billingAddress and shippingAddress fields and Add @Embedded annotation
 1.5 Create setter and getter method for the billingAddress and shippingAddress
 1.6 Refactoring SpringJPABootstrap.java

2. Add hibernate strategy in the resources/application.properties
 - spring.jpa.hibernate.naming-strategy=org.hibernate.cfg.DefaultComponentSafeNamingStrategy

3. Run and See the results

4. Review the H2 Database using H2-Console
 4.1 Customer Table
 4.2 User Table

